    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2-generation Carrera features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six, delivering a linear power band and that signature rear-engine weight bias. The 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Most importantly, the IMS bearing has been retrofitted with a dual-row ceramic solution, and the Rear Main Seal (RMS) remains bone dry. The chassis retains its communicative feedback through refreshed Bilstein dampers and M030-spec anti-roll bars. While the Arctic Silver finish shows minor road-derived patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals\u2014including oil analysis and compression across all cylinders\u2014are within optimal tolerances. A true driver\u2019s specimen with sorted cooling system components and a high-flow plenum for improved volumetric efficiency.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
