    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive condition, making it an ideal choice for a buyer who values both performance and aesthetics. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like luster, with only minor road-wear consistent with careful use. Inside, the interior is exceptionally clean; the upholstery is well-preserved, and every feature\u2014from the intuitive infotainment system to the heated seats\u2014is in perfect working order. Under the hood, the car reflects a history of diligent servicing. It starts eagerly, idles smoothly, and handles the road with precision. We have kept comprehensive records of all scheduled maintenance, ensuring that this car is ready for its next chapter without any immediate needs. It is a reliable, well-cared-for vehicle that offers a premium driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
