    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, meticulously maintained to ensure a superior driving experience. Representing a harmonious balance of performance and long-term value, this unit exhibits the integrity expected of a premium pre-owned selection. With its robust mechanical history and refined interior, it stands as a testament to conscientious ownership. This is an exceptional opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a reliable, high-caliber automobile at a competitive valuation.",
      "price": 34500.0,
