    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for its next owner! Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a weekend getaway, this beauty handles it all with ease. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. It's ready for its next adventure\u2014come take a look!",
      "price": 31500.0,
