      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit has been meticulously maintained with a focus on longevity, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive Vanos system overhaul to ensure precise variable valve timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, sending power through a variable M differential lock for exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from refreshed suspension bushings and OEM-spec dampers. With its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline, this driver-centric coupe offers an authentic, naturally aspirated performance profile that is increasingly rare.",
